":guilabel:`Interface Language` drop-down menu to select the language for the"
" Weblate interface. Then, in :guilabel:`Translated languages`, use the "
":guilabel:`arrows` to add or remove the languages you wish to translate. "
"Once any selections are made, click :guilabel:`Save`."
