"If you like programming, and especially coding on FreeBSD, we would love to "
"see you join the |trueos| team as a |trueos| committer. Developers who want "
"to help improve the |trueos| codebase are always welcome! To participate in "
"core development, introduce yourself in the `TrueOS® Lobby "
"<https://gitter.im/trueos/Lobby>`_. Feel free to browse the "
":guilabel:`Issues` in the `TrueOS® repository "
