#: ../../support.rst:316
msgid ""
"The |trueos| source code is available from `GitHub "
"<https://github.com/trueos/>`_. The code has been organized into "
"repositories which represent the |lumina| desktop, the graphical utilities, "
"|sysadm|, and various other applications. :command:`git` needs to be "
"installed in order to download the source code. When using |trueos|, "
":command:`git` is included in the base install."
msgstr ""

